We suggested a set of 5 reviewers in the SholarOne Manuscirpts application,
 with no preference.
 According to us, the five of them are relevant to review this paper.
 Four of them have themselves extracted pseudo-potentials in the past and
 Maurizio Persico has a broad culture in quantum chemistry, which makes
 him at ease with this kind of work.
\end_layout

